      "activityCount": 1,
      "description": "The Flying V Mandolin is a legendary instrument crafted by the divine hands of the Sun God Lux. This magical mandolin is made of shining golden wood with intricate carvings of sun rays and a golden inlay of a soaring phoenix at the center.As soon as a bard touches the Flying V Mandolin, they can feel the power of Lux coursing through their veins.\nThe mandolin glows with a bright golden light, and the user gains advantage on all performance checks made while playing it.The Flying V Mandolin also serves as a potent spell focus for bards, allowing them to cast spells with increased potency and range. When the user plays a spellcasting melody on the mandolin, the notes take flight, soaring towards their intended targets with incredible speed and accuracy.",
